title: I Like Food
lyrics:
I like food! Food tastes good! 
I like food! Food tastes good!
Juicy burgers, greasy fries,
Turkey legs and raw fish eyes
Teenage girls, with ketchup too!
Get out of my way, or I'll eat you
I like food, food tastes good!
I like food, food tastes good!

I'm going to turn dining back into eating

I like food! Food tastes good!
I like food! Food tastes good!
